        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. Is male or female â‰¥22 years of age at Visit 1;

          2. Wagnergrade 1 or 2 DFU;

          3. In the leg with the target ulcer has an ABI > 0.70 and < 1.20 OR if the ABI is >1.20
